snippet.title: MILITSIONER by TallBoys - Teaser
snippet.description:
We are ready to present an early look of our new project "Militsioner".
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1373530/Militsioner/
Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/tallboys

You’re a criminal who is planning an escape from the Giant-Policeman, while he’s trying to provoke you into actions that expose your guilt.


Twitter: https://twitter.com/mytallboys
